Package: cortar
Title: cortar: Single gene analysis of splice-junctions from RNA-seq
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Rhett", "Marchant", , "rmar4592@uni.sydney.edu.au", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-4817-9022"))
Description: Cortar extracts reads at the exon-intron junction from RNA-seq
    and reports the proportion of splicing events across each intron. By
    comparing these values to controls, deviations from normal splicing can
    be characterised in test samples.
